title: Ordinal-like transactions surge as gas fees go ‘crazy’ on Polygon network
description:
The proliferation of Ordinal-like transactions of PRC-20 tokens appears to have pushed gas fees on Polygon (MATIC), an Ethereum (ETH) layer-2 network, to yearly highs. title: APEC Meeting: Yellen Acknowledges Digital Assets’ Potential, Announces Regulation Advancements
